          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A renderer information object that describes all renderers able to drive the devices specified by the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "gdevs",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " parameter.  The function returns ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "NULL",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " if it fails for any reason. If an error occurs, call the function ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/aglGetError",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to determine what the error is.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This function normally returns a list of more than one renderer information objectâ€”one for each renderer found on the system. To access data in the first renderer information object tin the list, call the function ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/aglDescribeRenderer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". To access data in a renderer information object that is not the first one in the list, use ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.agl/documentation/AGL/aglNextRendererInfo",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
